italian net reserv rise in februari itali 's net offici reserv rose to 66,172 billion lire in februari 1987 from a previous report 62,174 billion in januari , the bank of itali said . gold hold at end-februari total 35,203 billion lire , unchang on januari . convert currenc total 18,467 billion lire , up from 14,899 billion in januari , while european currenc unit ( ecu ) hold were 10,156 billion lire against 10,133 billion .